1 AN ACT concerning crimes, punishment and criminal procedure; relating
2 to crimes against persons; limiting or prohibiting work release for
3 people an offender convicted of a second or third offense of domestic
4 battery; requiring an offender convicted of a first offense to undergo
5 a domestic violence offender assessment; amending K.S.A. 21-5414
6 and repealing the existing section.
